Oracle2's inaugural session. Massive fleet audit, infrastructure setup, multiple contributions pushed across SuperInstance repos.

## Contributions
- **constraint-theory-core**: Fixed 2 benchmark compile errors, cargo fix cleanup. 2 commits pushed to main. 261 tests passing.
